    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you won't believe your eyes when you see this beauty in person. It has been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and pampered since day one. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and babied, this is the one. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
