    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This AP2-generation roadster is a masterclass in mechanical purity, preserved in impeccable, turn-key condition. At its heart lies the F22C1 high-revving inline-four, featuring a forged rotating assembly and VTEC variable valve timing that remains crisp and decisive. Power is delivered through a precise, short-throw six-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains incredibly rigid thanks to the factory X-bone frame, while the four-wheel double-wishbone suspension retains its original geometry and damping characteristics. Every component, from the synchros to the subframe bushings, reflects a vehicle maintained to the highest standards of performance and aesthetic integrity.",
